Welcome To The LACI Project

Presentation of the LACI project

Like any project, no matter the field, it must respond to a problem whatever it may be.

The LACI project responds to a recurrent problem, which should however alarm any investor, that of the inflow of money. In all projects.
If the inflow of money only comes from one point, it is known that all this point of reference and where will become very unstable in time, making the project dependent on this point.

The LACI project solves this inherently simple and basic problem by providing a second money entry point that will itself focus on 4 diverse crypto only investment lines. This makes the project in perpetual evolution regardless of the entry point NÂ°1.

Tokenomic

A token economy where 90% of the tokens are available on PancakeSwap, a decentralized exchange platform (DEX), means that the majority of the token supply is available to traders and investors in the open market. This can create high liquidity for the token
The 5% of tokens distributed for the creator can be considered as a reward for the initial effort and investment.
The 3% of tokens distributed to the team of 4 technicians can be seen as a reward for their hard work and contribution to the development and maintenance of the platform or project related to crypto-currency. This distribution can help keep a technical team motivated and committed in the long run.
The remaining 2% of tokens are reserved for launching the LC token.

Company LACI

LACI is a pioneer in selling blockchain, smart contract and functional dapp tutorials for individuals and beginners. Blockchain is a cutting-edge technology that creates decentralized networks for transactions and data exchange. Thanks to its transparency and security, it offers numerous advantages in many fields.

At LACI, we believe that everyone should have access to the benefits of blockchain, regardless of their prior experience with the technology. That's why we've developed simple, practical tutorials to help beginners understand blockchain concepts and put them into practice. Our tutorials are accompanied by videos and clear graphics, which allow you to follow the step-by-step processes of creating and using blockchains.

In addition to tutorials, LACI also offers smart contracts and functional dapps for individuals and beginners. Smart contracts are autonomous contracts that are automatically executed based on certain predefined conditions. Dapps, or decentralized applications, are applications that run on a blockchain and offer security and transparency benefits. At LACI, we offer customized smart contracts and dapps, tailored to the specific needs of each client.

We are proud to be a company that helps make blockchain accessible to everyone. Our team is made up of blockchain and software development experts who work tirelessly to provide our customers with innovative and practical solutions. Whether you are a beginner or an experienced user, we are here to help you get the most out of blockchain. Trust LACI for all your blockchain solutions.
